  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p>Our client, a well-known MNC, specializing in the recovery, refining, and trading of precious and non-ferrousmetals is hiring for a sales executive. </p><p><br /><strong>Job Responsibilities: </strong></p><ul><li>Manage and grow relationships with existing clients, ensuring strong service quality and customer satisfaction.   </li><li>Drive new business development by identifying and engaging potential clients in the electrical/electronic manufacturing sector across Singapore and ASEAN.         </li><li>Provide consultative sales by understanding client production processes and proposing suitable industrial waste recycling or electronic materials solutions.      </li><li>Monitor industry trends, competitors, and precious‑metal market movements to provide strategic insights to management</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Job Responsibilities: </strong>      </p><ul><li>Minimum 5 years of sales experience, ideally in the manufacturing sector (electrical/electronics preferred). </li><li>Diploma or bachelor's degree in any field  <br /></li></ul><p>Interested applicant, please click APPLY or email me at jennifer.hardicar@jac-recruitment.com <br />Jennifer Maria Hardicar<br />JAC Recruitment Pte Ltd <br />EA LicenseNumber: 90C3026<br />EA Personnel: R1987984<br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p></p><p></p>",
